{"tid":483623,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助]年尾去東京有咩好做","createTime":"2017-11-29T09:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T05:33:53.000Z","uid":45616,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6dca9e083e411cc12c3ab532716155befe1ab4","tid":483623,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"對上一次去東京已經係小學四年班<br />\n今次同女朋友去<br />\n12月30號黃昏落機，1月4號凌晨走，住秋葉原。<br />\n<br />\n諗住落機Check in完就去秋葉原行下同晚飯算<br />\n31號夜晚諗住去東京鐵塔同增上寺倒數，日抖唔知有咩好做<br />\n附近晚飯有冇推薦?<br />\n<br />\n1月1號想去明治神宮參拜<br />\n同日去埋新宿+涉谷又會否好趕?<br />\n<br />\n其他日子都未有plan，因為新年好似好多野都唔開<br />\n想問上野同淺草一帶一日玩唔玩得晒?去埋晴空塔會唔會好趕?<br />\n<br />\n雪地插j跪求"},{"pid":"ebd0cefbedc9d6409a116966236a4f298b77d920","tid":483623,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新宿定原宿呀？"},{"pid":"efae8af0efb4234926f20721d307f5afd2873676","tid":483623,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新宿定原宿呀？</blockquote><br />\n如果涉谷+新宿+原宿 是咪一日搞唔掂?"},{"pid":"d64d1d995789a501741240f33f4d5f30c8c9c45d","tid":483623,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"神宮一個鐘內都行晒咁濟"},{"pid":"a1ce149a963b053884263405494d4eb8368e5312","tid":483623,"uid":2020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"1月1號至3號好似好多野都唔會開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540f7be711cd49301094b541416812707c448f6a","tid":483623,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:02:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新宿定原宿呀？</blockquote><br />\n如果涉谷+新宿+原宿 是咪一日搞唔掂?</blockquote><br />\n我覺得就<br />\n神宮（1-2hr)&gt;原宿（睇你條女睇幾耐,不過好撚多人，都唔會太快）&gt;涉谷都係睇係你行乜同行幾耐&gt;新宿就睇你係指行邊度"},{"pid":"b7edf0852fe3fcce3a78ff72012d0a984874c1e0","tid":483623,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新宿定原宿呀？</blockquote><br />\n如果涉谷+新宿+原宿 是咪一日搞唔掂?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你係想shopping定淨係四圍行下為主<br />\n<br />\n會買野既 新宿同原宿 夠你行成朝"},{"pid":"198aa0b8be308369dd2b48c8e055baaebba10b44","tid":483623,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"淺草就我覺得可以朝早行雷門，之後晴空塔，坐19船去台場又行下，浸下溫泉<br />\n（當然你想睇夜景另外一個玩法）<br />\n上野條街個人覺得冇乜嘢<br />\n行一兩個鐘啫"},{"pid":"1e0d65b694db433870a568719808e49ed0da6704","tid":483623,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淺草就我覺得可以朝早行雷門，之後晴空塔，坐19船去台場又行下，浸下溫泉<br />\n（當然你想睇夜景另外一個玩法）<br />\n上野條街個人覺得冇乜嘢<br />\n行一兩個鐘啫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晴士塔夜晚好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然上到去都唔覺得夜景靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可能係香港夜景太屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過係塔附近影真係幾靚"},{"pid":"658830baba81ceae16c9f95a51b2ddacc535122c","tid":483623,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淺草就我覺得可以朝早行雷門，之後晴空塔，坐19船去台場又行下，浸下溫泉<br />\n（當然你想睇夜景另外一個玩法）<br />\n上野條街個人覺得冇乜嘢<br />\n行一兩個鐘啫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晴空塔夜晚好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然上到去都唔覺得夜景靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可能係香港夜景太屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過係塔附近影真係幾靚</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f8f3af1578988857d991280b0662822132406201","tid":483623,"uid":56512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1月1號至3號好似好多野都唔會開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2號開始大部分都會開返<br />\n<br />\n淺草寺1號夜晚好熱鬧，個個去新年參拜，好多檔小食檔攤<br />\n<br />\n利申：上年年頭去"},{"pid":"8f31a4e7d288391bcbd713040368b395c36018c4","tid":483623,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淺草就我覺得可以朝早行雷門，之後晴空塔，坐19船去台場又行下，浸下溫泉<br />\n（當然你想睇夜景另外一個玩法）<br />\n上野條街個人覺得冇乜嘢<br />\n行一兩個鐘啫</blockquote><br />\n本來都有打算去台場大江戶<br />\n但我地兩個都有紋身唔入得<br />\n又唔係高達迷所以應該放棄<br />\n<br />\n諗緊朝早上野亞美+公園 &gt;中午到黃昏 雷門 &gt;晚上 晴空塔"},{"pid":"0d9e657d3c43c42445325496d24b79e5038e70e7","tid":483623,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新宿定原宿呀？</blockquote><br />\n如果涉谷+新宿+原宿 是咪一日搞唔掂?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你係想shopping定淨係四圍行下為主<br />\n<br />\n會買野既 新宿同原宿 夠你行成朝</blockquote><br />\n原宿同涉谷都mark左幾間店一定要去<br />\n咁可能放棄新宿先"},{"pid":"89a7e89fd103e62ced7847563e41dc43c79bd59a","tid":483623,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1月1號至3號好似好多野都唔會開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2號開始大部分都會開返<br />\n<br />\n淺草寺1號夜晚好熱鬧，個個去新年參拜，好多檔小食檔攤<br />\n<br />\n利申：上年年頭去</blockquote><br />\n如果係咁可能晚上晴空塔再過淺草<br />\n謝謝資訊"},{"pid":"74dcb84bef200adda91bbb456e235e36455209c8","tid":483623,"uid":23683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:17:51.000Z","msg":"邊個機場落機 預你6點半 出到去check in完 應該差唔多8點<br />\n秋葉原d鋪都開始關門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afed93d0244afd4d60c94e15d054a93aab72e75","tid":483623,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:17:58.000Z"